Hi all,I have a question that how to  judge the class type in typescript? pseudo-code as below:

```
function isComponent(ipt:any){
     if(ipt==Component) return true;
     return false;
}
function isAaComponent(ipt:any){
     if(ipt==AaComponent) return true;
