_Edit: I needed to remove the three dots! :)_

@DanielRosenwasser 

In the case missing arguments there is a simple alternative, perhaps only highlight the closing parenthesis or the last line of the call expression?

``` ts
function func(f: () => void, n: number) {}

func(() => {
